author: Source: Malvern Gazette
title: X Factor's Rita Ora booed during Six Chair Challenge - Malvern Gazette
text:
Judge Rita Ora was booed by the crowd following her decision to unseat contestant Karen Mav for Kiera Weathers during The X Factor's Six Chair Challenge. In the dramatic episode, 23-year-old Karen impressed with I'd Rather Go Blind by Etta James, but 18-year-old Kiera blew the panel away with Whitney Houston classic I Will Always Love You and was rewarded with a seat by Girls mentor Rita.
